column5: That area is number one on my list. May have to schedule a 2nd trip next year to be sure to get there. Thank you for the video. Really glad the weather is cooperating. Seems only fair after the late ice out. Keep them coming.
Thanks for the great video and congratulations on the nice size eyes. Makes me want to get to Lac Seul in September. Thanks Again, Mike Kansas
Nice video. Would of been better if little Jack would of been in it
